Prof. Itse Sagay (SAN), Chairman of the Presidential Advisory Commitee Against Corruption  (PACAC), has predicted landslide victory for President Muhammadu Buhari in Saturday’s presidential election. Sagay who spoke in a chat with Daily Independent said Buhari’s victory will forever bury the political aspiration of Atiku Abubakar, former Vice-president and presidential candidate of the Peoples Democratic Party (PDP) and former president Olusegun Obasanjo. “Buhari’s victory will be landslide, huge landslide.  He will bury Atiku and that will be the end of him. “He will also bury Obasanjo and that will be the last time he will poke out his nose on what doesn’t concern him,” he said.